<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: nefarious drone (mild) -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_mild.label>憎恶低语 (微弱)</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_mild.label>
  <!-- EN: It... is everywhere, coldly analyzing our every move. I want to escape this planet, but it... is everywhere! -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_mild.description>它...无处不在, 冷漠分析着我们的一举一动, 我想逃离这个星球, 可它...无处不在!</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_mild.description>
  <!-- EN: nefarious drone (strong) -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_strong.label>憎恶低语 (强烈)</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_strong.label>
  <!-- EN: Deceit... distortion... extremism... they are so numb, yet so decayed. In truth, we are all sick. -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_strong.description>欺瞒...扭曲...偏激...它们是如此的熟悉, 又如此的腐朽, 其实我们都病了.</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_strong.description> 
  <!-- EN: nefarious drone (intense) -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_intense.label>憎恶低语 (激烈)</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_intense.label>
  <!-- EN: I feel its hatred inside me, the way I feel my own emotions. The world is still so vast, yet my body is already too frail to endure. -->
  <NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_intense.description>我在心中能感受到它的恨意，仿佛我就是它, 世界还如此的广袤, 可我的躯壳羸弱疲惫.</NefariousDrone.stages.nefarious_drone_intense.description>
  
</LanguageData>